## Quick routing

| You are editing… | Surface |
|------------------|---------|
| Intake, consent, applicant chrome, victim routes | **1** |
| Advocate dashboard, org staff tools, case lists | **2** |
| Future state agency oversight UI | **3** |
| `app/admin/**` | **4** |

When in doubt, match **mental model** (guided vs CRM vs analytics vs console) before copying layout from another surface.
